When Suku bought our Honey Queen Bee Saree, Dhruv and I were so thrilled — she even picked a matching blouse fabric and inskirt to go with it. Dhruv added a cute little handwritten note inside her package because we’ve always loved her warmth and energy from afar.

We never expected her to wear it for Diwali, let alone share it. 🙈 But she did. And not just a post — she wore it with so much grace, made it her own, and gave Honey a whole new glow.

It’s these unexpected, genuine moments of connection that remind us why we started Anaira in the first place.

Thank you, @_beingsuku_ . You didn’t just wear our saree — you wore it with love. And that means the world to us 🤍✨
